.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/35900/', '', 'Ramipril, Valsartan, Rosuvastatin, Lisinopril, Perindopril, Niacin, Pravastatin, Acetylsalicylic acid, Ezetimibe, Bempedoic acid, Indapamide, More', 'Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Abatacept, Upadacitinib, Siponimod, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, Cladribine, Belumosudil, More', 1767369485);
